: UM/MOD 
	2DUP U< 
	IF NEGATE 15 
		FOR 
			>R DUP UM+ R> 
			R> DUP UM+ R> 
			+ DUP R> R@ SWAP 
			>R UM+ R> OR 
			IF >R DROP 1 + R> 
			ELSE DROP 
			THEN R> 
		NEXT 
		DROP SWAP EXIT 
	THEN DROP 2DROP -1 DUP ;


: M/MOD 
	DUP 0< DUP R> 
	IF NEGATE >R DNEGATE R> 
	THEN >R DUP 0< 
	IF R@ + 
	THEN R> UM/MOD R> 
	IF SWAP NEGATE SWAP 
	THEN ;

: ALIGNED 
	DUP 0 2 UM/MOD DROP DUP 
	IF 
		2 SWAP - 
	THEN 
	+ ;

: PACK$ 
	ALIGNED DUP >R OVER DUP 0 2 UM/MOD DROP - OVER + 0 SWAP ! 2DUP C! 1 + SWAP CMOVE R> ;

: EXTRACT 0 SWAP UM/MOD SWAP DIGIT ;
